WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:01:15.400

00:01:42.585 --> 00:01:45.305
In eight more hours, we will witness

00:01:45.385 --> 00:01:48.185
the grand reunification ceremony
of Hong Kong and China.

00:01:48.265 --> 00:01:52.345
This is a moment we have
been waiting for 155 years.

00:01:52.425 --> 00:01:53.025
WELCOME BACK, HONG KONG

00:01:53.105 --> 00:01:58.825
The midnight of July 1st, 1997
is approaching steadily.

00:02:10.065 --> 00:02:10.905
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

00:02:12.145 --> 00:02:15.425
What was it again? Good

00:02:15.505 --> 00:02:18.345
afternoon, Sir.

00:02:28.625 --> 00:02:31.185
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

00:02:46.385 --> 00:02:48.745
No parking here.

00:02:48.825 --> 00:02:51.265
No parking here. Go.

00:02:51.905 --> 00:02:52.985
‎Hey!

00:02:53.065 --> 00:02:54.785
Where did she go?

00:03:00.785 --> 00:03:03.865
A relative of someone here?

00:03:08.465 --> 00:03:10.385
Look. That guy.

00:03:10.465 --> 00:03:11.065
NEW YORK BLOCK

00:03:11.145 --> 00:03:12.225
Why is he in black?

00:03:22.905 --> 00:03:24.585
They didn't even pick up the kid
after they bumped into him.

00:03:42.425 --> 00:03:43.625
Qiang.

00:03:43.705 --> 00:03:44.625
Qiang.

00:03:51.105 --> 00:03:52.425
Eighteenth floor?

00:03:52.505 --> 00:03:54.465
I thought no one lived there anymore.

00:04:05.145 --> 00:04:06.105
Qiang.

00:04:12.865 --> 00:04:13.745
Do you see what's on her back…

00:04:13.825 --> 00:04:15.065
-What are you staring at?
-Oh my!

00:04:15.825 --> 00:04:16.825
Nothing.

00:04:17.905 --> 00:04:19.345
I have a meeting at the provincial office.

00:04:19.425 --> 00:04:21.105
Keep your eyes open.
Make sure nothing happens.

00:04:21.184 --> 00:04:22.225
Okay.

00:04:31.145 --> 00:04:33.065
The janitor said she went
to the 18th floor.

00:04:33.145 --> 00:04:34.425
18th floor? It's already haunted

00:04:34.505 --> 00:04:35.705
before they raided
the prostitution rings here.

00:04:35.785 --> 00:04:38.025
Eighteenth floor?
Wasn't the underground club raided?

00:04:38.105 --> 00:04:39.305
Where did they go?

00:05:29.785 --> 00:05:31.225
It's you, Ma Qiang?

00:05:32.065 --> 00:05:34.985
Weird. Both fire exits are locked.

00:05:35.065 --> 00:05:36.905
Where could those two have gone?

00:05:36.985 --> 00:05:39.465
Don't touch anything.
Go downstairs to find them.

00:05:41.745 --> 00:05:42.985
What's the matter, Wang?

00:05:48.105 --> 00:05:50.465
Wang Wuluan. What are you doing?

00:06:00.505 --> 00:06:02.865
Why is there a pair of footprints here?

00:06:34.945 --> 00:06:36.145
There's no one in there.

00:06:44.825 --> 00:06:49.465
Call 110!

00:07:00.145 --> 00:07:03.345
Puking before you go to work.

00:07:03.425 --> 00:07:07.505
This must be your first day, rookie.

00:07:07.585 --> 00:07:10.065
I'm getting motion sickness.
You drove too fast.

00:07:10.145 --> 00:07:14.345
Liu. After you're done puking,
come here. I want to talk to you.

00:07:14.425 --> 00:07:16.985
Come here. I want to talk to you.

00:07:20.705 --> 00:07:21.865
Listen.

00:07:25.665 --> 00:07:26.545
Listen.

00:07:26.625 --> 00:07:29.065
We've been asked
to team up at the last minute.

00:07:29.145 --> 00:07:32.185
Even though it's quite ad hoc,
rules must be established.

00:07:32.265 --> 00:07:34.545
I know. Captain Feng said
you came to assist

00:07:34.625 --> 00:07:35.905
and would go back after a week.

00:07:35.985 --> 00:07:37.145
-They asked me to…
-They asked you

00:07:37.225 --> 00:07:38.705
not to give me any trouble. Right?

00:07:39.985 --> 00:07:42.025
They asked me to guide you
through our work.

00:07:43.065 --> 00:07:46.065
Who's guiding whom now? You're a rookie.

00:07:46.145 --> 00:07:48.025
Do you know how many years
I've been doing this?

00:07:50.385 --> 00:07:51.825
But you've been working
in a police station.

00:07:51.905 --> 00:07:53.585
I studied for six years to become
a criminal police officer.

00:07:55.105 --> 00:07:56.545
You only know the theories.

00:07:56.625 --> 00:07:58.065
Enough chatting.

00:07:58.145 --> 00:08:00.705
The old guide the young.
That's the rule in the squad.

00:08:00.785 --> 00:08:02.785
Captain Feng only told me
to partner up with you.

00:08:02.865 --> 00:08:05.305
Even in a partnership,
there's a pecking order.

00:08:05.385 --> 00:08:06.985
I'm the mentor. You're my apprentice.

00:08:07.065 --> 00:08:09.225
When we work, you listen to me.

00:08:14.505 --> 00:08:16.625
So, how do you want to proceed today?

00:08:16.705 --> 00:08:17.905
That's the right attitude.

00:08:17.985 --> 00:08:21.745
Listen. I was in charge of Yuanlongli
when I was working in the police station.

00:08:21.825 --> 00:08:24.145
Back then, the workers dug out a cenotaph.

00:08:24.225 --> 00:08:27.985
After that, the residents
became paranoid and superstitious.

00:08:28.065 --> 00:08:29.665
They keep calling the police for nothing.

00:08:30.265 --> 00:08:33.105
-So?
-So, we stay put.

00:08:33.185 --> 00:08:34.664
We let them cool their heads.

00:08:34.745 --> 00:08:36.105
I disagree.

00:08:36.185 --> 00:08:39.904
If paranoia isn't solved in time,
it might evolve into a collective risk.

00:08:39.985 --> 00:08:42.425
Did I just establish
the pecking order for nothing?

00:08:42.505 --> 00:08:44.585
I'm your mentor. You're my apprentice.

00:08:44.665 --> 00:08:46.425
-If I tell you to do this…
-Mr. He.

00:08:46.505 --> 00:08:48.265
Can we work now?

00:08:48.865 --> 00:08:51.865
Mr… Mr. He? You think I'm a mechanic?

00:08:51.945 --> 00:08:53.585
More like someone who fixes gas lights.

00:08:53.665 --> 00:08:54.705
What gas lights?

00:08:54.785 --> 00:08:56.545
Gaslighting. Gaslight.

00:08:56.625 --> 00:08:58.105
Did you just tell me to bugger off?

00:08:58.665 --> 00:09:00.625
So rude.

00:09:05.785 --> 00:09:09.025
Something bad happened
in Yuanlongli just now.

00:09:09.625 --> 00:09:12.545
Do you want to know?
A woman was carrying a man on her back

00:09:12.625 --> 00:09:14.665
up to the 18th floor.

00:09:14.745 --> 00:09:16.185
How creepy!

00:09:16.265 --> 00:09:17.865
A man and a woman.

00:09:17.945 --> 00:09:20.345
Both covered in black.

00:09:20.425 --> 00:09:21.265
Gone.

00:09:21.345 --> 00:09:23.305
Not even bones left.

00:09:23.385 --> 00:09:25.385
I saw with my own eyes.

00:09:25.465 --> 00:09:26.985
You saw with your own eyes.

00:09:29.025 --> 00:09:30.785
Meng. Come here.

00:09:34.465 --> 00:09:37.865
Not even bones left. I see.

00:09:37.945 --> 00:09:40.785
Officer He. That's my cloak.

00:09:40.865 --> 00:09:42.625
Didn't you say it killed two people?

00:09:42.705 --> 00:09:43.745
It's now evidence.

00:09:43.825 --> 00:09:46.425
I have to keep it to examine it.

00:09:46.505 --> 00:09:48.265
Who else witnessed it?

00:09:48.345 --> 00:09:49.985
‎YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

00:09:53.105 --> 00:09:55.385
‎POLICE

00:09:56.465 --> 00:09:58.425
Calling the police
for the slightest inconvenience.

00:09:58.505 --> 00:09:59.705
How many times has it been?

00:09:59.785 --> 00:10:01.305
You two.

00:10:01.385 --> 00:10:02.905
One is from the residents committee.
One is from the security team.

00:10:02.985 --> 00:10:05.985
Instead of dispelling
the superstition, you fanned it.

00:10:06.065 --> 00:10:08.265
Making a fake police call is a crime.
Do you understand?

00:10:08.345 --> 00:10:09.745
Yes.

00:10:09.825 --> 00:10:11.945
There's no victim and no culprit.

00:10:12.025 --> 00:10:13.465
Their relatives
also didn't call the police.

00:10:13.545 --> 00:10:15.225
There's nothing to file a case here.

00:10:15.305 --> 00:10:17.105
Besides, the police already came here.

00:10:17.185 --> 00:10:19.465
Come. Sign it.

00:10:21.025 --> 00:10:23.945
One more week,
and I'll go back to my previous post.

00:10:24.025 --> 00:10:26.305
Do you get what I mean?

00:10:26.385 --> 00:10:28.025
It's the last sprint.

00:10:28.105 --> 00:10:30.785
Don't go to the criminal department
and bother me for something trivial.

00:10:30.865 --> 00:10:32.025
If I get a case,
I won't be able to go back.

00:10:32.945 --> 00:10:34.705
-Just sign it.
-I… Where do I sign it?

00:10:37.025 --> 00:10:38.305
This young man is…

00:10:39.145 --> 00:10:41.385
Oh, he's Liu. My apprentice.

00:10:41.465 --> 00:10:43.025
He just graduated.
It's his first day at work.

00:10:43.105 --> 00:10:45.305
He's new here.
Do look after him, will you?

00:10:46.665 --> 00:10:49.025
Hello. I'm Ran. R-A-N.

00:10:49.985 --> 00:10:51.145
Also, I'm not his…

00:10:57.905 --> 00:10:59.665
WITNESS' STATEMENT

00:11:03.585 --> 00:11:05.305
Hi. Are you Li Tieling?

00:11:05.905 --> 00:11:08.305
So the woman and the old man
disappeared when you turned around.

00:11:08.945 --> 00:11:11.745
Yes. The woman was wearing a white dress
and blue leather heels.

00:11:11.825 --> 00:11:13.425
She vanished just like that.

00:11:13.505 --> 00:11:15.785
-Do you want to know how they vanished?
-Yes.

00:11:15.865 --> 00:11:18.105
Re-enact what you did
when you chased the rickshaws away.

00:11:18.185 --> 00:11:19.145
Then turn around and look at me.

00:11:19.225 --> 00:11:23.385
Okay. No parking here. Go. Go.

00:11:23.465 --> 00:11:24.305
Are you insane?

00:11:25.345 --> 00:11:26.225
Then I…

00:11:28.505 --> 00:11:30.665
He's gone. He's gone.

00:11:30.745 --> 00:11:32.065
I'm here.

00:11:34.385 --> 00:11:35.785
You assumed they would cross
the main road to enter the gate.

00:11:35.865 --> 00:11:37.105
But they stuck to the wall,

00:11:37.825 --> 00:11:38.865
just outside your line of vision.

00:11:40.265 --> 00:11:41.665
This is called a psychological blind spot.

00:11:41.745 --> 00:11:43.185
Watch me do it again.

00:11:43.265 --> 00:11:45.625
You explained the trick.

00:11:45.705 --> 00:11:47.625
Why bother doing it again?

00:11:50.185 --> 00:11:51.585
It's called re-enactment.

00:11:51.665 --> 00:11:53.105
According to the Western
investigation procedures,

00:11:53.185 --> 00:11:56.225
you must imagine that you're the culprit
and re-enact what they did.

00:11:56.305 --> 00:11:57.545
Enact what?

00:11:57.625 --> 00:11:58.905
Re… enact?

00:12:01.625 --> 00:12:04.305
From this place to that block,
taking the main road is the shorter route.

00:12:05.265 --> 00:12:07.025
Why did they take a detour then?

00:12:08.265 --> 00:12:09.345
Come with me.

00:12:12.625 --> 00:12:13.985
Where are we going?

00:12:14.945 --> 00:12:16.385
Case closed.

00:12:16.465 --> 00:12:18.025
They didn't ask for criminal police.

00:12:18.105 --> 00:12:20.625
Captain Feng got a call and asked us
to assess the situation personally.

00:12:20.705 --> 00:12:22.585
We didn't even enter the premises.
Isn't that too irresponsible?

00:12:22.665 --> 00:12:24.345
Irresponsible?

00:12:24.425 --> 00:12:26.345
Making a fake police call
is irresponsible.

00:12:26.425 --> 00:12:27.745
It's a waste of police resources too.

00:12:28.745 --> 00:12:32.585
Sir, we over-reacted here. Please go back.

00:12:32.665 --> 00:12:33.905
I'll just talk to Officer Qu.

00:12:33.985 --> 00:12:35.785
Wait. Officer Qu?

00:12:35.865 --> 00:12:37.665
Which one? Qu Dahai?

00:12:37.745 --> 00:12:42.065
Yes. I called 110, and Officer Qu came.

00:12:42.145 --> 00:12:42.985
He's inside the building?

00:12:44.665 --> 00:12:45.665
I'll go and take a look.

00:12:52.705 --> 00:12:55.425
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

00:12:57.745 --> 00:12:59.905
That woman carried the old man

00:12:59.985 --> 00:13:02.705
and stood still here.
She even took off her heels.

00:13:03.345 --> 00:13:04.345
What else did she do?

00:13:08.945 --> 00:13:09.865
She did this.

00:13:14.105 --> 00:13:15.145
I can fix it.

00:13:22.185 --> 00:13:23.065
I'll pick it up.

00:13:32.665 --> 00:13:35.105
So clumsy. Hurry up.

00:13:40.545 --> 00:13:42.985
Officer Qu. Careful. The footprints.

00:13:50.425 --> 00:13:51.465
What are you doing?

00:13:52.065 --> 00:13:53.225
PATTIA CLUB

00:13:53.305 --> 00:13:56.185
He Yuanhang. What brings you here?

00:13:57.065 --> 00:13:59.185
Han. Shouhu.

00:13:59.265 --> 00:14:01.665
What are you doing here? Go back.

00:14:01.745 --> 00:14:02.625
Did I say you could go back?

00:14:02.705 --> 00:14:03.665
Continue.

00:14:03.745 --> 00:14:05.505
Your footsteps are making a mess.

00:14:05.585 --> 00:14:08.745
Are you examining
or contaminating the crime scene?

00:14:08.825 --> 00:14:10.225
Who says I'm examining the scene?

00:14:10.305 --> 00:14:12.425
I'm looking for the culprit. Continue!

00:14:13.785 --> 00:14:15.145
Touch anything if you dare.

00:14:15.225 --> 00:14:17.625
Excuse me. You're blocking the evidence.

00:14:20.185 --> 00:14:22.465
See? The criminal police are working.

00:14:22.545 --> 00:14:23.745
Now work!

00:14:24.665 --> 00:14:25.865
You little…

00:14:38.265 --> 00:14:40.945
I like him. What's his name?

00:14:43.905 --> 00:14:45.705
Ran Fangxu. My apprentice.

00:14:45.785 --> 00:14:47.305
Top scorer from People's Public Security
University of China, PPSUC.

00:14:47.385 --> 00:14:48.505
PPSUC?

00:14:49.705 --> 00:14:51.105
Your apprentice?

00:14:51.185 --> 00:14:53.065
Why would I have
brought him here with me, otherwise?

00:14:54.105 --> 00:14:54.945
Jealous?

00:14:55.705 --> 00:14:57.785
Want to join the criminal department?

00:14:57.865 --> 00:14:59.505
I can talk to Captain Feng for you.

00:15:00.265 --> 00:15:02.505
You can have him.

00:15:03.145 --> 00:15:04.305
Sounds good?

00:15:14.505 --> 00:15:16.545
This wooden plank is so annoying.

00:15:17.305 --> 00:15:18.785
Well, it's all thanks to your mentor.

00:15:18.865 --> 00:15:20.665
He did this when he raided
the prostitution ring.

00:15:20.745 --> 00:15:21.945
That's right.

00:15:26.185 --> 00:15:27.025
Let me borrow this.

00:15:29.505 --> 00:15:30.745
He is not my mentor.

00:15:34.465 --> 00:15:36.225
You liar.

00:15:38.625 --> 00:15:39.785
-Ma Qiang.
-Yes.

00:15:39.865 --> 00:15:41.705
-Open the door.
-Okay.

00:15:49.065 --> 00:15:50.705
Forgive me. I conducted an experiment.

00:15:50.785 --> 00:15:51.785
What are you doing?

00:15:52.745 --> 00:15:55.305
Seriously? It's called enaction. Right?

00:15:57.705 --> 00:15:59.665
Re-enactment.

00:16:01.745 --> 00:16:03.345
There's a nail on the door frame.

00:16:03.425 --> 00:16:05.025
The dust by the door frame is gone.

00:16:05.105 --> 00:16:08.145
I suppose someone
hung the black cloak here.

00:16:10.865 --> 00:16:12.985
The height of it is enough
to cover an adult

00:16:13.065 --> 00:16:14.745
when someone opens the door.

00:16:15.785 --> 00:16:16.905
A prank then?

00:16:17.625 --> 00:16:18.745
But there's one unanswered question.

00:16:18.825 --> 00:16:20.505
The footprints disappear here.

00:16:20.585 --> 00:16:22.385
They didn't go back the way they came.

00:16:23.025 --> 00:16:25.225
Qu Dahai and his men stepped
all over the place.

00:16:25.305 --> 00:16:26.425
How can we trace footprints now?

00:16:26.505 --> 00:16:27.705
Dust can be thick.

00:16:27.785 --> 00:16:30.105
New and old footprints have gaps.

00:16:30.185 --> 00:16:32.025
You're so thorough, Fangxu.

00:16:32.105 --> 00:16:33.145
You left no stone unturned.

00:16:33.225 --> 00:16:36.305
Unlike someone I know
who has peanuts for a brain.

00:16:36.385 --> 00:16:37.465
All empty inside.

00:16:37.545 --> 00:16:39.425
You have peanuts for a brain.

00:16:39.505 --> 00:16:40.345
Move.

00:16:41.545 --> 00:16:43.785
How can you be a criminal police
with such a bad core strength?

00:16:46.425 --> 00:16:48.265
Size 37 feet.

00:16:48.945 --> 00:16:52.025
Carrying an old man
all the way from outside.

00:16:53.225 --> 00:16:55.185
She must be a strong woman.

00:16:57.505 --> 00:17:00.345
These must be the basics
you learned in PPSUC.

00:17:00.425 --> 00:17:01.865
They don't teach you common sense.

00:17:04.985 --> 00:17:06.025
You little…

00:17:15.905 --> 00:17:16.985
What did you see?

00:17:22.305 --> 00:17:23.625
Four cigarette butts.

00:17:23.704 --> 00:17:25.345
Judging from their looks,

00:17:25.424 --> 00:17:27.464
they were used less than two hours ago.

00:17:27.985 --> 00:17:31.665
Judging from the charred ends,
the smoker was anxious.

00:17:31.745 --> 00:17:33.705
Some of them were thrown away
after a few puffs were taken.

00:17:35.465 --> 00:17:37.025
Do you recognize the brand?

00:17:37.105 --> 00:17:38.385
How much does it cost?

00:17:41.825 --> 00:17:43.625
A packet of Yuxi cigarettes.

00:17:43.705 --> 00:17:46.305
Mainly for bosses.
Twenty yuan for one packet.

00:17:53.985 --> 00:17:57.385
Are you sure there were
no footprints in the room?

00:17:57.465 --> 00:17:58.945
I guess so.

00:18:01.345 --> 00:18:02.705
We came looking for the culprit.

00:18:02.785 --> 00:18:04.345
Of course, we walked around.

00:18:05.345 --> 00:18:09.865
Then don't walk that much.

00:18:19.065 --> 00:18:22.545
‎BEIJING TRAVEL

00:18:27.785 --> 00:18:28.625
Officer He. Officer Qu.

00:18:28.705 --> 00:18:30.505
Calm down. Tell me clearly.

00:18:30.585 --> 00:18:34.625
Okay. I checked all the rooms.
There's no one.

00:18:34.705 --> 00:18:37.425
I also checked the security cameras.
No one took the elevator.

00:18:37.505 --> 00:18:41.625
Two adults couldn't possibly
vanish just like that.

00:18:41.705 --> 00:18:43.065
They must be somewhere.

00:18:43.145 --> 00:18:44.985
Both sides of the staircase
are locked from the outside too.

00:18:45.065 --> 00:18:45.905
Where else could they go?

00:18:46.705 --> 00:18:48.985
It looks like a locked room.

00:18:49.745 --> 00:18:51.505
Three paths.

00:18:52.505 --> 00:18:53.745
The staircase is locked.

00:18:53.825 --> 00:18:56.025
The elevator has security cameras.

00:18:56.105 --> 00:19:00.105
Exactly. It's weird.
That's why I called Captain Feng.

00:19:00.825 --> 00:19:04.825
I think you should file a case.

00:19:05.945 --> 00:19:07.905
File what case? What case?

00:19:07.985 --> 00:19:09.745
Let me explain everything to you.

00:19:10.345 --> 00:19:13.185
The door is locked from the outside.
You can't open it.

00:19:25.865 --> 00:19:29.225
See? They left like this.

00:19:29.305 --> 00:19:30.865
This door isn't locked.

00:19:30.945 --> 00:19:32.505
File a case?

00:19:32.585 --> 00:19:34.465
This is just a prank. Okay?

00:19:34.545 --> 00:19:36.545
Officer He. This isn't right.

00:19:36.625 --> 00:19:38.425
The staircase. The window.

00:19:38.505 --> 00:19:40.545
And the padlock. The padlock!

00:19:41.305 --> 00:19:42.505
What? Isn't it…

00:19:45.625 --> 00:19:47.505
-Surround them from both sides!
-On it!

00:19:59.545 --> 00:20:00.945
Stay right there!

00:20:03.865 --> 00:20:04.945
Wait for me.

00:20:05.025 --> 00:20:07.465
Sorry, I'm in a hurry.
Take the next one. Sorry.

00:20:07.545 --> 00:20:08.865
Stealing a lock before the police.

00:20:08.945 --> 00:20:10.385
How dare you!

00:20:10.465 --> 00:20:11.585
Stop right there.

00:20:12.305 --> 00:20:14.505
Stop right there. Stop right there.

00:20:15.265 --> 00:20:16.265
What are you doing?

00:20:45.025 --> 00:20:45.945
He Yuanhang!

00:20:46.025 --> 00:20:48.225
I caught him. He Yuanhang! Help me!

00:20:48.305 --> 00:20:49.465
Why are you yelling?

00:20:50.265 --> 00:20:51.105
Stop yelling.

00:20:51.185 --> 00:20:52.505
You took the elevator,
but you're still slow!

00:20:52.585 --> 00:20:53.785
He has already run away!

00:21:00.865 --> 00:21:02.145
Be careful.

00:21:02.225 --> 00:21:03.145
NEW YORK BLOCK

00:21:03.225 --> 00:21:04.785
Officer He!

00:21:07.025 --> 00:21:08.985
Officer He. Officer He.

00:21:09.065 --> 00:21:10.665
There are bad guys in the block.

00:21:10.745 --> 00:21:12.345
They scared my son.

00:21:13.905 --> 00:21:16.065
Were you running around
the staircase just now?

00:21:17.865 --> 00:21:19.745
Why did you go to the 18th floor?

00:21:19.825 --> 00:21:21.585
He saw everything.

00:21:21.665 --> 00:21:23.745
He even bumped into them.

00:21:23.825 --> 00:21:24.905
Tell me.

00:21:24.985 --> 00:21:27.705
Why did you lock us in the staircase?

00:21:27.785 --> 00:21:29.905
I was scared you'd come after me.

00:21:32.945 --> 00:21:34.745
Hey there. It's okay.

00:21:34.825 --> 00:21:37.105
You saw the two missing persons, right?

00:21:37.985 --> 00:21:40.105
I saw their hands.

00:21:40.625 --> 00:21:43.145
It's not human hands. They have claws.

00:21:52.985 --> 00:21:53.905
Claws?

00:21:53.985 --> 00:21:56.225
Is that coming from your exaggeration?

00:22:02.145 --> 00:22:04.465
See? I told you so.

00:22:04.545 --> 00:22:06.545
They bumped into him,

00:22:06.625 --> 00:22:08.105
and they didn't even pick him up.

00:22:08.185 --> 00:22:10.505
They bumped into him how many times?

00:22:10.585 --> 00:22:11.425
Just once.

00:22:11.505 --> 00:22:13.105
And he got bruises everywhere?

00:22:13.185 --> 00:22:14.905
It's as if he has been run over.

00:22:14.985 --> 00:22:18.185
-Little one, your bruises are…
-I fell when he chased after me.

00:22:26.825 --> 00:22:29.025
Officer He. Listen.

00:22:29.105 --> 00:22:31.025
We put the padlock
when we were checking the place.

00:22:31.105 --> 00:22:33.945
I don't care who put it there.
I just want to know if it was locked.

00:22:34.025 --> 00:22:35.145
No, it wasn't.

00:22:36.185 --> 00:22:37.065
It wasn't locked?

00:22:37.145 --> 00:22:39.625
That means those two people
could leave through that door.

00:22:40.385 --> 00:22:41.505
I guess so.

00:22:47.625 --> 00:22:48.625
You examined the place for hours,

00:22:48.705 --> 00:22:51.305
and you couldn't figure out
one simple staircase.

00:22:51.385 --> 00:22:53.625
Qu. Given your lack of competence,

00:22:53.705 --> 00:22:55.425
how am I supposed
to put in a few good words for you?

00:22:56.225 --> 00:22:57.185
Say no more.

00:22:59.225 --> 00:23:02.545
Don't just stand there.
This is just a prank.

00:23:02.625 --> 00:23:03.985
Go back and pack up. Case closed!

00:23:05.345 --> 00:23:07.225
I already told you so.

00:23:07.305 --> 00:23:09.265
The reunification of Hong Kong
is more interesting.

00:23:13.465 --> 00:23:15.625
Officer He. We need to file a case.

00:23:25.625 --> 00:23:27.665
Then explain. Why?

00:23:27.745 --> 00:23:30.425
Ma Qiang said there were
no footprints in the western corridor.

00:23:30.505 --> 00:23:32.865
They also said the cloak
took two people away.

00:23:32.945 --> 00:23:34.425
They make things up all the time.

00:23:34.505 --> 00:23:35.585
How can I believe them?

00:23:35.665 --> 00:23:37.385
Be patient. Let me finish.

00:23:37.465 --> 00:23:39.705
Just tell me what you want to do.

00:23:40.505 --> 00:23:42.465
I just want to get to the bottom
of this case.

00:23:42.545 --> 00:23:44.945
Listen carefully.
One, this isn't even a case.

00:23:45.025 --> 00:23:48.665
Two, if you want to investigate,
find another partner. Don't…

00:23:48.745 --> 00:23:50.425
Don't bother you as you're about
to go back to being the deputy director.

00:23:50.505 --> 00:23:51.825
I get it.

00:23:51.905 --> 00:23:53.625
I knew you were that kind of person
from the start.

00:23:53.705 --> 00:23:55.185
Just gaslighting people.

00:24:01.545 --> 00:24:04.305
Did you scold me just now?

00:24:14.625 --> 00:24:17.425
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

00:24:24.505 --> 00:24:29.345
WEIYANG PUBLIC SECURITY BUREAU
NANSHAN BRANCH

00:24:36.825 --> 00:24:37.985
‎This one is…

00:24:44.505 --> 00:24:46.225
Kid.

00:24:46.305 --> 00:24:48.225
Did you see Ran?

00:24:48.305 --> 00:24:50.585
Lan? Who?

00:24:50.665 --> 00:24:53.025
R-A-N.

00:24:53.105 --> 00:24:54.065
You must be new here.

00:24:54.145 --> 00:24:56.225
-I…
-He Yuanhang. Stop yelling.

00:24:56.305 --> 00:24:57.545
Can't you see we're working here?

00:24:57.625 --> 00:24:59.385
I'm looking for Ran.

00:25:00.745 --> 00:25:02.425
Something happened in Yuanlongli again?

00:25:02.505 --> 00:25:04.065
Go back to your work.

00:25:04.145 --> 00:25:06.305
Don't pester me.

00:25:08.465 --> 00:25:11.385
Ran Fangxu is slacking
in the archive room.

00:25:11.985 --> 00:25:13.465
Do talk to him.

00:25:15.265 --> 00:25:16.665
He could've answered my call.

00:25:16.745 --> 00:25:18.025
I called him for five minutes.

00:25:18.105 --> 00:25:19.745
All of them are so lazy.

00:25:21.025 --> 00:25:22.385
He is Mr. He.

00:25:28.465 --> 00:25:31.465
Old Geezer. Why are you here again?

00:25:31.545 --> 00:25:33.905
Don't call me old geezer.

00:25:33.985 --> 00:25:35.025
Where is Ran?

00:25:37.025 --> 00:25:37.945
Why do you need him?

00:25:39.465 --> 00:25:41.265
It's none of your business. Where is he?

00:25:47.545 --> 00:25:49.305
You eat to sleep, sleep to eat.

00:25:49.385 --> 00:25:51.145
Where's your spirit?

00:25:51.225 --> 00:25:53.505
Everyone gets bored
when they work here every day.

00:25:54.745 --> 00:25:56.105
Why don't you ask them
to put me on patrol duty?

00:25:56.185 --> 00:25:57.545
Ran Fangxu!

00:25:58.105 --> 00:25:59.585
MEN'S TOILETS

00:26:19.585 --> 00:26:21.665
UNDER MAINTENANCE

00:26:21.745 --> 00:26:22.985
Ran Fangxu!

00:26:28.745 --> 00:26:29.745
Ran Fangxu!

00:26:29.825 --> 00:26:31.065
Just because you're standing
on the toilet bowl

00:26:31.145 --> 00:26:32.705
doesn't mean I won't know you're here.

00:26:32.785 --> 00:26:34.505
Come out. Open the door.

00:26:34.585 --> 00:26:36.745
Sir. I have diarrhea.

00:26:36.825 --> 00:26:38.025
I'm vomiting and pooping.

00:26:38.105 --> 00:26:39.585
I can't go anywhere.

00:26:39.665 --> 00:26:41.745
Are you an ostrich
that poops while standing?

00:26:41.825 --> 00:26:43.305
Come out now.

00:26:43.385 --> 00:26:44.625
I'll count to three.

00:26:44.705 --> 00:26:47.065
Count to 300, and I still won't come out.

00:26:47.145 --> 00:26:48.265
Just you wait.

00:26:49.145 --> 00:26:50.425
-One.
-Sir.

00:26:50.945 --> 00:26:51.905
-Two.
-What are you doing?

00:26:51.985 --> 00:26:52.905
-Sir?
-Three!

00:27:00.185 --> 00:27:01.425
Hey!

00:27:04.225 --> 00:27:05.825
Sir,

00:27:05.905 --> 00:27:07.825
I just finished this lesson plan.

00:27:08.945 --> 00:27:13.185
Oh, you and your useless theories again.

00:27:13.785 --> 00:27:16.625
I have a case that concerns my reputation.

00:27:17.305 --> 00:27:18.265
You have a reputation?

00:27:18.345 --> 00:27:19.745
I'll tell you on the way.

00:27:21.185 --> 00:27:22.945
Sir, I have work to do.

00:27:23.025 --> 00:27:24.745
Bah! This is what you call work?

00:27:24.825 --> 00:27:27.425
Some people love to be on patrol duty.

00:27:27.505 --> 00:27:29.945
Some people just want to stay
in the archive room.

00:27:30.545 --> 00:27:32.385
I can't catch a break at all.

00:27:33.425 --> 00:27:34.705
What are you implying?

00:27:41.145 --> 00:27:42.065
Mister,

00:27:42.585 --> 00:27:43.945
can you drive slower?

00:27:45.305 --> 00:27:46.385
Slower?

00:27:46.945 --> 00:27:49.505
Back then, on our first gig together,

00:27:50.305 --> 00:27:53.665
I drove slightly faster
and you got your panties in a twist.

00:27:55.265 --> 00:27:57.825
I… I have motion sickness.

00:27:58.545 --> 00:28:02.185
Besides, it wasn't like you drove fast
to investigate the case.

00:28:03.065 --> 00:28:04.465
Nonsense!

00:28:04.545 --> 00:28:07.065
Don't make it sound
like I'm irresponsible.

00:28:08.865 --> 00:28:11.225
When we first worked together,

00:28:11.305 --> 00:28:13.265
you didn't even bother memorizing
my surname.

00:28:14.065 --> 00:28:15.145
I…

00:28:26.825 --> 00:28:28.865
All right. This is it.

00:28:29.465 --> 00:28:30.665
I'm not driving over there.

00:28:30.745 --> 00:28:32.425
That place brings bad luck.

00:28:33.985 --> 00:28:34.945
Pay up.

00:28:35.025 --> 00:28:36.105
Okay.

00:28:36.185 --> 00:28:37.225
Let's go.

00:28:39.225 --> 00:28:41.145
You didn't tell me
we'd come to Yuanlongli.

00:28:41.745 --> 00:28:44.105
Come on. If I told you,
you wouldn't want to come with me.

00:28:44.185 --> 00:28:45.465
Come down now.

00:28:45.545 --> 00:28:47.225
I'm just here on a business trip.

00:28:47.305 --> 00:28:48.985
I'll be back after a week.

00:28:49.585 --> 00:28:51.385
You're going back to Beijing after a week?

00:28:52.505 --> 00:28:54.625
Did you bring me with you
for another case?

00:29:03.945 --> 00:29:05.625
His name is Han Zi'ang.

00:29:05.705 --> 00:29:07.585
He went missing less than 48 hours ago.

00:29:07.665 --> 00:29:08.705
They haven't filed the case yet.

00:29:08.785 --> 00:29:10.985
I've talked to the parents,

00:29:11.065 --> 00:29:13.465
and I think there's more
than meets the eye.

00:29:13.545 --> 00:29:15.545
I agreed to help them.

00:29:16.105 --> 00:29:19.385
After all these years, I've become
quite good at finding missing persons.

00:29:19.465 --> 00:29:21.985
They call me human radar.

00:29:22.705 --> 00:29:24.785
If there's more to the case
than meets the eye,

00:29:24.865 --> 00:29:26.225
then hand the case over to the police.

00:29:26.305 --> 00:29:28.345
As I said, they haven't
filed the case yet.

00:29:28.425 --> 00:29:31.625
I'm just a kind citizen who wants
to locate the missing child.

00:29:31.705 --> 00:29:33.865
Since we're here already,
just help me out.

00:29:33.945 --> 00:29:38.865
-My reputation is at stake here.
-Sir, I'm a teacher now.

00:29:38.945 --> 00:29:41.025
And you're retired.
We can't investigate cases anymore.

00:29:41.105 --> 00:29:42.505
Let's just leave.

00:29:42.585 --> 00:29:43.785
Don't give me excuses.

00:29:43.865 --> 00:29:45.145
Eighteen years ago,

00:29:45.225 --> 00:29:47.065
I too was eager to leave after a week.

00:29:47.145 --> 00:29:50.105
But a jerk came to me
and said I was irresponsible.

00:29:56.425 --> 00:29:57.865
Sorry, sir.

00:29:58.665 --> 00:29:59.865
Back then, it was my fault.

00:30:02.505 --> 00:30:05.465
It's not your fault.
It's not anyone's fault.

00:30:05.545 --> 00:30:07.185
If I must put the blame on something,

00:30:07.265 --> 00:30:09.705
it's on the fact that you didn't build
a good relationship with me.

00:30:11.785 --> 00:30:13.865
I didn't build
a good relationship with you?

00:30:13.945 --> 00:30:15.945
-I kept addressing you as my mentor then.
-Nonsense!

00:30:16.025 --> 00:30:17.865
Stop wasting my time. Get out of the car.

00:30:21.225 --> 00:30:23.585
Slow down. Slow down.

00:30:27.305 --> 00:30:30.145
You keep saying that you don't
want to come to Yuanlongli.

00:30:30.225 --> 00:30:33.025
But once you're in here,
you walk briskly like an eager visitor.

00:30:34.825 --> 00:30:36.385
That's because
you were gaslighting me again.

00:30:37.345 --> 00:30:40.625
I see you're not on social media.
It's not called gaslighting anymore.

00:30:40.705 --> 00:30:42.705
It's called brainwashing. Come.

00:30:46.145 --> 00:30:47.905
Let's take a break.

00:30:47.985 --> 00:30:50.465
Don't. We can't stay here for long.

00:30:50.545 --> 00:30:54.625
This building is haunted.
Once in a while, it'll kill someone.

00:30:54.705 --> 00:30:56.025
Two policemen died here.

00:30:56.105 --> 00:30:56.945
Died here?

00:30:57.025 --> 00:30:58.825
One of them was in charge of this place.

00:30:58.905 --> 00:31:01.305
-What's his name again?
-He something.

00:31:01.385 --> 00:31:03.385
When they found him, his body was impaled

00:31:03.465 --> 00:31:06.265
by a spear on this wall.

00:31:06.345 --> 00:31:07.505
It was horrifying.

00:31:08.545 --> 00:31:10.065
Quickly now.

00:31:10.145 --> 00:31:12.425
You two look horrifying.

00:31:12.505 --> 00:31:15.505
Mister. We weren't even talking about you.
Why are you yelling at me?

00:31:16.305 --> 00:31:18.185
-Sir.
-Don't hold me back.

00:31:18.265 --> 00:31:21.785
Tell me. How was I impaled on this wall?

00:31:28.505 --> 00:31:30.225
Oh my…

00:31:38.825 --> 00:31:42.905
Sir, Yuanlongli houses
a superstitious community.

00:31:42.985 --> 00:31:44.305
You know that already.

00:31:44.385 --> 00:31:45.785
Why pick a bone with them?

00:31:45.865 --> 00:31:49.105
If I don't scold them now,
the next one they curse will be you.

00:31:57.785 --> 00:31:59.425
You're dead.

00:31:59.505 --> 00:32:01.785
You can't step on the 18th floor.

00:32:01.865 --> 00:32:03.545
Yuanlongli

00:32:03.625 --> 00:32:09.065
-Eighteenth floor, 18 pillars
-Eighteenth floor…

00:32:09.145 --> 00:32:14.585
Eighteenth floor with 18 pillars

00:32:14.665 --> 00:32:19.705
Eighteen pillars
With 18 men to carry them…

00:32:21.105 --> 00:32:22.825
They are still singing the nursery rhyme?

00:32:22.905 --> 00:32:26.545
If you hadn't insisted
on investigating the truth,

00:32:26.625 --> 00:32:30.145
this so-called haunted building
would've taken more lives.

00:32:31.145 --> 00:32:36.345
Eighteenth floor with 18 pillars

00:32:36.425 --> 00:32:41.465
Eighteen bodies, 18 heads

00:32:52.825 --> 00:32:53.865
He Yuanhang.

00:32:54.665 --> 00:32:55.665
You owe me a meal.

00:32:55.745 --> 00:32:56.825
For what?

00:32:56.905 --> 00:32:59.905
WEIYANG CULTURAL CENTER

00:32:59.985 --> 00:33:01.225
Aren't you investigating a case?

00:33:01.305 --> 00:33:03.825
I jumped the queue for you
and got the report ready.

00:33:05.665 --> 00:33:08.265
Six more days till I return
to the police station.

00:33:08.345 --> 00:33:09.345
What case is this?

00:33:10.145 --> 00:33:11.785
Come on. They sent
the evidence for analysis.

00:33:12.385 --> 00:33:13.585
Two sets of fingerprints.

00:33:13.665 --> 00:33:14.585
Four cigarette butts.

00:33:14.665 --> 00:33:17.465
One cloak. And one security footage.

00:33:17.545 --> 00:33:19.105
It's all under your name.

00:33:22.225 --> 00:33:23.065
I…

00:33:24.105 --> 00:33:25.145
It was all good.

00:33:26.505 --> 00:33:30.065
Except Mr. He Yuanhang
and I don't get along well.

00:33:30.145 --> 00:33:32.145
Can you get me another partner?

00:33:32.225 --> 00:33:33.945
Changing your partner on your first day?

00:33:34.025 --> 00:33:35.185
What did He Yuanhang do?

00:33:35.265 --> 00:33:36.905
I don't think he has…

00:33:38.065 --> 00:33:40.625
Captain Feng. I'm here
to find my apprentice.

00:33:41.265 --> 00:33:42.465
Let me reiterate.

00:33:42.545 --> 00:33:43.745
I am not your apprentice.

00:33:43.825 --> 00:33:47.785
Young and petty.
It's just a term. No need to overreact.

00:33:47.865 --> 00:33:50.265
I'm not being petty.
I'm being responsible here.

00:33:51.185 --> 00:33:52.945
Captain Feng. See this?

00:33:53.025 --> 00:33:55.185
Our temperaments don't match.
Our personalities are different.

00:33:55.265 --> 00:33:57.465
We argue often,
and that'll affect our work efficiency.

00:33:57.545 --> 00:33:59.465
Since I'm going back
to the police station,

00:33:59.545 --> 00:34:01.705
why don't you give him another partner?

00:34:01.785 --> 00:34:03.865
I'll hand over whatever I'm doing to him.

00:34:08.304 --> 00:34:11.025
I see you two are putting
on an act in front of me.

00:34:12.264 --> 00:34:15.824
Just be frank. What help
do you need from me?

00:34:15.905 --> 00:34:17.344
Captain Feng.

00:34:17.425 --> 00:34:19.505
This is not an act.

00:34:19.585 --> 00:34:22.945
-I mean it. I want to break…
-Break up!

00:34:26.945 --> 00:34:28.425
-Captain Feng.
-I am.

00:34:34.625 --> 00:34:37.985
Captain Feng. The embarrassing case
from Yuanlongli.

00:34:38.065 --> 00:34:39.824
The residents have come forward.

00:34:39.905 --> 00:34:40.784
What now?

00:34:40.865 --> 00:34:43.264
He Yuanhang. Mind your words.

00:34:45.264 --> 00:34:49.025
Maybe officers like you
think it's nothing.

00:34:49.105 --> 00:34:51.784
But the residents are getting manic.

00:34:51.865 --> 00:34:55.344
They are saying the two missing persons
are the Black and White Guards.

00:34:55.425 --> 00:34:56.824
And the building is their hunting ground.

00:34:57.905 --> 00:34:59.825
And they are singing this.

00:34:59.905 --> 00:35:01.225
Yuanlongli

00:35:01.305 --> 00:35:02.785
Eighteenth floor

00:35:02.865 --> 00:35:04.425
Eighteen bodies, 18 heads

00:35:04.505 --> 00:35:05.425
Nonsense.

00:35:05.505 --> 00:35:07.745
Someone among them
is trying to spread a rumor.

00:35:10.345 --> 00:35:11.665
Captain Feng.

00:35:11.745 --> 00:35:15.665
When they were building Yuanlongli,
they found a tomb.

00:35:15.745 --> 00:35:17.225
It was a cenotaph
from the Three Kingdoms period.

00:35:17.305 --> 00:35:18.505
There were no human remains inside.

00:35:18.585 --> 00:35:21.425
The Residents Committee
just has to clarify the rumors.

00:35:21.505 --> 00:35:24.025
Why mobilize the criminal police?

00:35:24.105 --> 00:35:28.585
The problem is that Yuanlongli
is a complex neighborhood.

00:35:29.145 --> 00:35:31.025
You see all sorts of people there.

00:35:31.865 --> 00:35:33.345
Someone went missing yesterday.

00:35:33.425 --> 00:35:34.545
Then today, a nursery song
like that appeared.

00:35:34.625 --> 00:35:36.385
Everyone is scared.

00:35:36.465 --> 00:35:39.185
-Please help us find the truth.
-He Yuanhang.

00:35:40.945 --> 00:35:44.265
What was yesterday's case about?

00:35:44.345 --> 00:35:47.105
Qu Dahai had already determined
that it was just a prank.

00:35:47.185 --> 00:35:49.345
-But I…
-It wasn't a prank at all.

00:35:50.545 --> 00:35:51.465
Captain Feng.

00:35:52.665 --> 00:35:54.265
I interviewed the witnesses last night.

00:35:54.345 --> 00:35:55.465
I can confirm three things.

00:35:55.545 --> 00:35:58.585
One. There are no footprints
deeper into the corridor.

00:35:58.665 --> 00:36:00.585
Two. The security guards
put the padlock there.

00:36:00.665 --> 00:36:03.905
Three. Mr. Liang broke the glass
of the door leading to the staircase.

00:36:03.985 --> 00:36:06.945
Therefore, the exit path
Officer He described yesterday

00:36:07.025 --> 00:36:08.545
could never have existed.

00:36:08.625 --> 00:36:11.105
The disappearance of those two persons
is still an enigma.

00:36:15.385 --> 00:36:17.665
Well said! I agree with Fangxu.

00:36:17.745 --> 00:36:18.825
I also agree with him.

00:36:18.905 --> 00:36:21.905
Trivial problems, when neglected,
will fester into major problems.

00:36:23.385 --> 00:36:24.945
Rumors can be destructive.

00:36:38.985 --> 00:36:41.985
Some say that He Yuanhang
only got into the criminal department

00:36:42.065 --> 00:36:43.345
because of his connections.

00:36:43.425 --> 00:36:44.625
Take a seat.

00:36:46.665 --> 00:36:51.265
But in fact, I chose him
from among many candidates.

00:36:51.345 --> 00:36:52.625
Captain Feng.

00:36:52.705 --> 00:36:55.385
Even though he never receives
proper training,

00:36:55.465 --> 00:36:59.185
the place he's in charge of consistently

00:36:59.265 --> 00:37:00.985
has the highest clearance rate.

00:37:01.065 --> 00:37:02.705
What does this mean?

00:37:02.785 --> 00:37:07.105
It means he has something
neither of us has.

00:37:08.665 --> 00:37:11.065
In certain areas,
he will be quite helpful.

00:37:11.665 --> 00:37:16.865
But of course, you can also
help him with your expertise.

00:37:16.945 --> 00:37:18.305
Do you get what I mean now?

00:37:19.865 --> 00:37:22.385
Captain Feng,
about the case in Yuanlongli…

00:37:22.465 --> 00:37:25.465
Both of you will follow up with the case.

00:37:27.785 --> 00:37:29.985
Officer He. Don't let me keep you.
I have to go now.

00:37:30.905 --> 00:37:35.025
‎POLICE BY THE PEOPLE
‎FOR THE PEOPLE

00:37:44.745 --> 00:37:48.745
MISSING DOG

00:38:08.905 --> 00:38:09.945
Stop.

00:38:11.105 --> 00:38:12.265
Rewind a bit.

00:38:15.625 --> 00:38:16.745
Here.

00:38:21.985 --> 00:38:24.145
It looks like a cigarette.

00:38:24.225 --> 00:38:26.505
Can you tell which brand it is?

00:38:29.065 --> 00:38:31.585
No. No way.

00:38:33.065 --> 00:38:34.025
No way.

00:38:43.745 --> 00:38:44.705
It looks like

00:38:46.185 --> 00:38:48.105
marks left by a medical paste.

00:38:53.505 --> 00:38:54.505
What are you doing?

00:38:54.585 --> 00:38:56.225
Did I sign this before you gave it
to the Forensic Department?

00:38:56.305 --> 00:38:57.985
Is the Forensic Department
strapped for cash lately?

00:38:58.065 --> 00:39:00.065
He Yuanhang! We're not done studying it.

00:39:00.145 --> 00:39:01.185
What does studying it serve?

00:39:02.225 --> 00:39:03.065
Hey!

00:39:07.545 --> 00:39:10.105
MISSING PERSONS

00:39:14.945 --> 00:39:16.265
MISSING PERSONS

00:39:16.345 --> 00:39:19.225
FEMALE: AROUND 20-25 YEARS OLD
MALE: AROUND 55-60 YEARS OLD

00:39:21.025 --> 00:39:23.465
This is your number?

00:39:23.545 --> 00:39:25.065
Yes. Should I use yours?

00:39:25.745 --> 00:39:27.145
I don't have a pager.

00:39:27.225 --> 00:39:28.665
Why do you not want to stay
in the criminal department?

00:39:28.745 --> 00:39:29.945
You're too naive.

00:39:33.105 --> 00:39:34.385
Officer He.

00:39:34.465 --> 00:39:37.705
I believe we should first figure out
the motive behind their disappearance.

00:39:37.785 --> 00:39:39.945
Isn't it clear enough? It's a prank.

00:39:40.545 --> 00:39:41.705
Then tell me.

00:39:41.785 --> 00:39:43.705
Why did the woman take off her heels
when she entered the elevator?

00:39:43.785 --> 00:39:46.225
And why did she hold the heels
with her teeth?

00:39:46.305 --> 00:39:48.945
Why did the old man press all the buttons
in the elevator before he left?

00:39:49.025 --> 00:39:50.865
Because it's a prank. Understood?

00:39:50.945 --> 00:39:53.065
Then why did they disappear
in that locked space?

00:39:53.145 --> 00:39:54.585
-Why, why, why.
-Why did they…

00:39:54.665 --> 00:39:56.345
Do you only know how to repeat why?

00:39:56.425 --> 00:39:59.225
Our priority should be to find out
how they disappear in Yuanlongli.

00:39:59.305 --> 00:40:01.185
That's redundant.

00:40:01.265 --> 00:40:04.185
Find them, and you'll know
how they disappear.

00:40:04.265 --> 00:40:05.505
Listen to me.

00:40:05.585 --> 00:40:08.665
Find them, and they
will give you the answer.

00:40:10.745 --> 00:40:11.905
Why should I listen to you?

00:40:13.985 --> 00:40:15.145
Fine.

00:40:18.465 --> 00:40:21.745
NANSHAN TYPEWRITING

00:40:22.665 --> 00:40:23.625
Wait.

00:40:24.345 --> 00:40:26.025
You see those rickshaw riders?

00:40:27.105 --> 00:40:28.945
Should we have a wager?

00:40:29.025 --> 00:40:30.025
Go to them.

00:40:30.105 --> 00:40:32.185
If you can get their names,

00:40:32.265 --> 00:40:34.065
I'll take orders from you.

00:40:34.145 --> 00:40:35.505
If you fail to do that,

00:40:35.585 --> 00:40:37.385
you take orders from me.

00:40:37.465 --> 00:40:38.465
What do you say?

00:40:39.665 --> 00:40:40.665
No, thanks.

00:40:43.465 --> 00:40:45.665
Didn't you want to find out how they left?

00:40:45.745 --> 00:40:48.825
I remember the missing persons
came on a rickshaw.

00:41:01.145 --> 00:41:02.625
Mister, where do you want to go?

00:41:02.705 --> 00:41:03.545
Mister, where do you want to go?

00:41:03.625 --> 00:41:05.665
-Mister, where do you want to go?
-Mister, where do you want to go?

00:41:05.745 --> 00:41:07.385
Hello, everyone.

00:41:07.465 --> 00:41:09.065
I am from the criminal department
of Nanshan police station.

00:41:09.145 --> 00:41:10.665
I'd like to know…

00:41:12.065 --> 00:41:12.985
Hey!

00:41:14.785 --> 00:41:15.825
Hey…

00:41:18.305 --> 00:41:19.505
Mister!

00:41:21.585 --> 00:41:22.545
Mister!

00:41:31.265 --> 00:41:33.945
Do you understand why I didn't leave
the police station's number?

00:41:34.025 --> 00:41:36.145
You look like an imperial envoy
who visits a village.

00:41:36.225 --> 00:41:38.185
Wearing a pair of slacks
won't make it easier to catch a criminal.

00:41:38.265 --> 00:41:39.745
You look posh.

00:41:39.825 --> 00:41:41.625
You speak like an officer,

00:41:41.705 --> 00:41:43.985
and you couldn't even get the names
of those rickshaw riders.

00:41:44.065 --> 00:41:45.825
You're telling me you want
to investigate the case?

00:41:49.465 --> 00:41:52.185
Officer He, when I was studying,

00:41:52.265 --> 00:41:54.625
I looked into renowned cases of missing
persons, both local and international.

00:41:54.705 --> 00:41:56.945
Specifically, their psychology
and behavior.

00:41:57.025 --> 00:41:59.865
My judgment tells me that
the Yuanlongli case isn't just a prank.

00:42:00.465 --> 00:42:05.425
Have you looked into the missing person
case in Weinan Street, Weiyang City?

00:42:07.345 --> 00:42:08.185
No.

00:42:08.265 --> 00:42:09.705
Do you know why?

00:42:11.025 --> 00:42:13.265
After I was assigned
to Weiyang, for 22 years,

00:42:13.345 --> 00:42:17.185
whenever someone or even a pet

00:42:17.265 --> 00:42:21.825
in my district went missing,
I could find them with my eyes closed.

00:42:21.905 --> 00:42:24.825
I didn't need to study
renowned missing person cases.

00:42:25.465 --> 00:42:28.745
But hanging up posters
and waiting for calls is too passive.

00:42:28.825 --> 00:42:30.945
And your initiatives
bring trouble to others.

00:42:31.025 --> 00:42:32.265
To whom?

00:42:32.345 --> 00:42:34.185
When you sent the evidence
to the Forensic Department,

00:42:34.265 --> 00:42:35.425
why did you leave my name?

00:42:37.305 --> 00:42:40.265
I only came here yesterday.
They won't acknowledge my signature.

00:42:44.185 --> 00:42:46.505
Get out of the car.
Get yourself back to the station

00:42:46.585 --> 00:42:48.585
and withdraw all analysis requests
under my name.

00:42:50.825 --> 00:42:52.905
Take me to Yuanlongli.
I'll examine the scene again.

00:42:52.985 --> 00:42:54.865
Did I owe you a favor? Get out of the car.

00:42:54.945 --> 00:42:56.905
It's an official vehicle.
Why should I leave?

00:42:56.985 --> 00:42:58.225
Official vehicle?

00:42:58.305 --> 00:42:59.785
This is my personal car.

00:42:59.865 --> 00:43:01.425
I paid for the petrol from my own pocket.

00:43:01.505 --> 00:43:03.185
And I printed these things
with my own money.

00:43:03.265 --> 00:43:06.465
You think you're the only one
with integrity? I have it too.

00:43:07.865 --> 00:43:09.305
Get out of the car.

00:43:10.625 --> 00:43:11.745
Officer He.

00:43:11.825 --> 00:43:13.745
Based on my deduction,

00:43:13.825 --> 00:43:15.745
the unusual behavior
from those two missing persons

00:43:15.825 --> 00:43:18.305
seems to be motivated
by some external coercion.

00:43:18.385 --> 00:43:20.465
Many homicides also started
as a missing person case.

00:43:20.545 --> 00:43:22.065
What homicide?

00:43:22.145 --> 00:43:24.745
There has never been a murder on my turf.

00:43:24.825 --> 00:43:27.065
You came, and there's a murder
all of a sudden.

00:43:28.385 --> 00:43:31.145
Murphy's law. Whatever you don't
want to happen will happen.

00:43:31.225 --> 00:43:33.385
I don’t care about your law.
I don’t care about your homicide.

00:43:33.465 --> 00:43:35.425
You lost the bet just now.

00:43:35.505 --> 00:43:38.145
So you take orders from me.
I now order you to return to the station

00:43:38.225 --> 00:43:40.345
and withdraw the analysis requests
under my name.

00:43:40.425 --> 00:43:41.345
He Yuanhang!

00:43:42.425 --> 00:43:43.825
You do not have what it takes
to be a criminal police officer.

00:44:39.825 --> 00:44:44.545
PATTIA CLUB, THAI MASSAGE